---
description: Default rules for the HBI codebase
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- Main app uses uv: run Python and pytest with `uv run` (or `.venv` after `uv sync` at repo root). IQE uses `Pipfile.iqe` and pipenv (`./setup-iqe.sh`, `unset PIPENV_PIPFILE` before main-app uv commands).
- When making changes, always test your code and make fixes as needed.
